title: ConvertXtoDVD 3.0.0.9 FINAL + Patch (19th April 2008)
description:
ConvertXtoDVD 3.0.0.9 Installation Instructions
	-----------------------------------------------


 1: Uninstall any previous versions of the program.


 2: Install vsoConvertXtoDVD3_setup, DO NOT START PROGRAM.


 3: Copy the 2 patch files to the following program directory:


    C:Program FilesVSOConvertX3


    Make sure to overwrite the existing files.


 4: The program is now registered and ready to use.


 5: Enjoy !!



 >> Enjoy The Program And Please Seed As Much As You Can <<
